{"tid":282974,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"fresh grad 搵唔到自己果行既工","createTime":"2017-06-13T18:51:34.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-18T12:11:03.000Z","uid":76223,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"49cf9a82426b1fe5fa17885002a0799f2f5b3647","tid":282974,"uid":76223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-13T18:51:34.000Z","msg":"有冇今年fg巴絲已經搵到一份自己果行/適合自己既工？<br />\n<br />\n我自問係一個好性急 好多憂慮既人<br />\n做左半個月廢青已經頂唔順要去搵工<br />\n宜家啱啱開始做part time <br />\n但同我讀果樣係無關係<br />\n屋企人叫我搵返我讀果行既工<br />\n如果唔係會後悔 <br />\n但我果行收入低 難搵工 又唔穩定<br />\n好擔心搵唔到 亦唔知應唔應該搵果行<br />\n<br />\n求巴絲分享/一齊傾計"},{"pid":"8c23697c3914824e588d6acbbbf9733ee42b8525","tid":282974,"uid":80097,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-13T18:55:32.000Z","msg":"你讀邊科丫？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0567ff4f25eed75a72d7ce8a0dedd96cd859df0","tid":282974,"uid":76223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-13T18:56:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你讀邊科丫？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nMedia <br />\n人地眼中既垃圾科<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"caf38341910a716b1c3ea4991cd6327fbd405221","tid":282974,"uid":31261,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-13T18:58:52.000Z","msg":"放心啦 無論而家簡做邊行 以後都會後悔"},{"pid":"080a93c6afa46eec622f3dfe86dd2c3bc4b6e16a","tid":282974,"uid":119920,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-13T19:02:29.000Z","msg":"其實我覺得最緊要係你自己想做d咩㗎姐<br />\n驚唔知做唔做好嘅，咪試下先咯<br />\n啱啱grad咋嘛，大把青春時間去試<br />\n試完唔ok先再打算咯<br />\nYou got nothing to lose<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申：都係fresh grad ，搵緊工"},{"pid":"954a23fded26e915a335d988361f7fbffac95ba1","tid":282974,"uid":76223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-18T07:24:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實我覺得最緊要係你自己想做d咩㗎姐<br />\n驚唔知做唔做好嘅，咪試下先咯<br /